{"article_id":"BovjdzjkG08whaE5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Several months before the coronavirus pandemic began ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the Trump administration eliminated a key American public health position in Beijing","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"intended to help detect disease outbreaks in China ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"has learned .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The American disease expert , a medical epidemiologist","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"embedded in China ' s disease control agency ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"left her post in July ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"according to four sources with knowledge of the issue .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The first cases of the new coronavirus may have emerged as early as November ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"as cases exploded ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the Trump administration in February chastised China","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"for censoring information about the outbreak","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"and keeping U.S. experts from entering the country","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"to help .","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"\" It was heartbreaking to watch , \"","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"said Bao-Ping Zhu , a Chinese American","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"who served in that role ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"which was funded by the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention , between 2007 and 2011 .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" If someone had been there ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"public health officials and governments across the world could have moved much faster . \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Zhu and the other sources said","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"the American expert , Dr. Linda Quick , was a trainer of Chinese field epidemiologists","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"who were deployed to the epicenter of outbreaks","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to help track , investigate and contain diseases .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"As an American CDC employee ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"they said ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Quick was in an ideal position","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to be the eyes and ears on the ground for the United States and other countries on the coronavirus outbreak ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and might have alerted them to the growing threat weeks earlier .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"No other foreign disease experts were embedded","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"to lead the program","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"after Quick left in July ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"according to the sources .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Zhu said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"an embedded expert can often get word of outbreaks early ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"after forming close relationships with Chinese counterparts .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Zhu and the other sources said","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Quick could have provided real-time information to U.S. and other officials around the world during the first weeks of the outbreak ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"when they said","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"the Chinese government tamped down on the release of information","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"and provided erroneous assessments .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"Quick left amid a bitter U.S. trade dispute with China","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"when she learned","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"her federally funded post ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"officially known as resident adviser to the U.S. Field Epidemiology Training Program in China ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"would be discontinued as of September ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"the sources said .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"The U.S. CDC said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"it first learned of a \" cluster of 27 cases of pneumonia \" of unexplained origin in Wuhan , China , on Dec. 31 .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Since then , the outbreak of the disease","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"known as COVID-19","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"has spread rapidly worldwide ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"killing more than 13,600 people ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"infecting more than 317,000 .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"The epidemic has overwhelmed healthcare systems in some countries ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"including Italy ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"and threatens to do so in the United States and elsewhere .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"During a press briefing on Sunday","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"shortly after this story was first published ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"President Donald Trump dismissed the report as similar to other stories regarding the CDC","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that he described as \" 100 percent wrong , \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"without addressing","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"whether the role had been eliminated .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"U.S. CDC Director Dr. Robert Redfield maintained","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the agency ' s presence in China \" is actually being augmented","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"as we speak , \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"without elaborating .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"In a statement to","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"before the report was published ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the CDC said","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"the elimination of the adviser position did not hinder Washington ' s ability","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"to get information","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"and \" had absolutely nothing","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"to do","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"with CDC not learning of cases in China earlier . \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"The agency said","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"its decision","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"not to have a resident adviser","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"\" started well before last summer","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and was due to China ' s excellent technical capability and maturity of the program . \"","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"The CDC said","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"it has assigned two of its Chinese employees as \" mentors \"","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to help with the training program .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"The agency did not respond to questions about the mentors ' specific role or expertise .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"The CDC would not make Quick ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"who still works for the agency ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"available for comment .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Asked for comment on Chinese transparency and responsiveness to the outbreak ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"China ' s Ministry of Foreign Affairs referred to remarks by spokesman Geng Shuang on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Geng said","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"the country \" has adopted the strictest , most comprehensive , and most thorough prevention and control measures in an open , transparent , and responsible manner ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and informed the","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"( World Health Organization )","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"and relevant countries and regions of the latest situation in a timely manner . \"","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"One disease expert told","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"he was skeptical","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"that the U.S. resident adviser would have been able to get earlier or better information to the Trump administration ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"given the Chinese government ' s suppression of information .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"\" In the end ,","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"based on circumstances in China ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"it probably wouldn ' t have made a big difference ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"\"","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Scott McNabb ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"who was a CDC epidemiologist for 20 years","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"and is now a research professor at Emory University .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"\" The problem was how the Chinese handled it .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"What should have changed was the Chinese should have acknowledged it earlier","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"and didn ' t . \"","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Alex Azar , secretary of Health and Human Services","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"( HHS )","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"said on Friday","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that his agency learned of the coronavirus in early January ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"based on Redfield ' s conversations with \" Chinese colleagues . \"","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Redfield learned","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"that \" this looks to be a novel coronavirus \" from Dr. Gao Fu , the head of the China CDC ,","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"according to an HHS administration official ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"\" Dr . Redfield always talked to Dr. Gao , \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"the official said .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"HHS and CDC did not make Azar or Redfield available for comment .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Zhu and other sources said","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"U.S. leaders should not have been relying on the China CDC director for alerts and updates .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"In general ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"they said ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"officials in China downplayed the severity of the outbreak in the early weeks","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"and did not acknowledge evidence of person-to-person transmission until Jan. 20 .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"After the epidemic exploded","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"and China had imposed strict quarantines ,","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Trump administration officials complained","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"that the Chinese had censored information about the outbreak","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"and that the United States had been unable to get American disease experts into the country","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"to help contain the spread .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Azar told CNN on Feb. 14","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"that he and CDC director Redfield officially offered to send a CDC team into China on Jan. 6","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"but still had not received permission","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"for them to enter the country .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"HHS oversees the CDC .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"\" Dr . Redfield and I made the offer on January 6th - 36 days ago , 60,000 cases and 1,300 deaths ago , \"","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Azar said .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"\" We made the offer","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"to send the CDC experts in","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"to assist their Chinese colleagues","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"to get to the bottom of key scientific questions like ,","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"how transmissible is this disease ?","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"What is the severity ?","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"What is the incubation period","depth":16},{"id":148,"text":"and can there be asymptomatic transmission ? \"","depth":16},{"id":149,"text":"Days later , the World Health Organization secured permission","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"to send a team","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"that included two U.S. experts .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"The team visited between Feb. 16th and 24th .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"By then , China had reported more than 75,000 cases .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"On Feb. 25 , the first day","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"the CDC told the American public to prepare for an outbreak at home ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo accused China of mishandling the epidemic through its \" censorship \" of medical professionals and media .","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"Relations between the two countries have deteriorated since then ,","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"as Trump has labeled the coronavirus the \" Chinese virus \"","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"- a description","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"the Chinese have condemned as stigmatizing .","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"Last week , the Chinese government announced","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"that Americans from three U.S. news organizations , The New York Times , Washington Post and Wall Street Journal , would be expelled from China .","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"The decision","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"to eliminate Quick ' s job","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"came","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"as the CDC has scaled back the number of U.S. staffers in China over the last two years ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"the sources told .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"\" We had already withdrawn many technical public health experts , \"","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"the same expert said .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"The CDC , however , disputed","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"that staffing was a problem","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"or that its information had been limited by the move .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"\" It was not the staffing shortage","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"that limited our ability \"","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"it said .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"The U.S. CDC team in Beijing now includes three American citizens in permanent roles , an additional American","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"who is temporary","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"and around 10 Chinese nationals ,","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"the agency said .","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"Of the Americans , one is an influenza expert with expertise in respiratory disease .","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"COVID-19 is not influenza ,","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"though it can cause severe respiratory illness .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"The CDC team , aside from Quick , was housed at U.S. Embassy facilities .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"No American CDC staffer besides Quick was embedded with China ' s disease control agency ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"the sources said .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"China in recent weeks has reported a dramatic slowdown in new cases , the result of drastic containment measures","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"including the lockdown of Hubei province , home to 60 million people .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"Nevertheless ,","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"the infectious disease experts","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"who spoke with","depth":16},{"id":191,"text":"said ,","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"the United States could use people like Quick with contacts on the ground ,","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"especially if fears of a second wave of infections materializes .","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"Thomas R. Frieden , a former director of the CDC , said","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"if the U.S. resident adviser had still been in China ,","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"\" it is possible that we would know more today about how this coronavirus is spreading and what works best","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"to stop it . \"","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"Dr. George Conway , a medical epidemiologist","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"who knows Quick","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"and had served as resident advisor between 2012 and 2015 ,","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"funding for the position had been tenuous for years","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"because of a perennial debate among U.S health officials","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"over whether China should be paying for funding its own training program .","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"Yet","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"since the training program was launched in 2001 ,","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"the sources familiar with it say ,","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"it has not only strengthened the ranks of Chinese epidemiologists in the field ,","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"but also fostered collegial relationships between public health officials in the two countries .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"\" We go there as credentialed diplomats","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"and return home as close colleagues and often as friends , \"","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"Conway said .","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"In 2007 , Dr. Robert Fontaine , a CDC epidemiologist and one of the longest serving U.S. officials in the adviser ' s position , received China ' s highest honor for outstanding contributions to public health due to his contribution as a foreigner","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"in helping to detect and investigate clusters of pneumonia of unknown cause .","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"But since last year ,","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"Frieden and others said ,","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"growing tensions between the Trump administration and China ' s leadership have apparently damaged the collaboration .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"\" The message from the administration was , ' Don ' t work with China ,","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"they ' re our rival , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"Frieden said .","depth":10},{"id":222,"text":"Trump ' s re-election campaign sent out a statement Sunday evening","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"dismissing controversy about the CDC ' S cut as a matter of politics .","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"\" Democrats are eager to politicize the coronavirus crisis","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"and weaponize it against President Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"the statement said .","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"\" In so doing , they ' re siding with the Chinese","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"and providing cover for Beijing ' s cover-up . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":457,"left":0,"right":456,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":456,"left":286,"right":455,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":270,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":236,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":232,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":231,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":1,"right":230,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":234,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":233,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":233,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":248,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":242,"right":247,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":9,"right":241,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":10,"right":240,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":11,"right":239,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":12,"right":238,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":13,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":245,"right":246,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":16,"right":244,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":17,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":251,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":22,"right":250,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":23,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":255,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":254,"right":30,"relation":"jo